text: Fambaré Ouattara Natchaba (17 April 1945. - 15 October 2020) was a Togolese politician. He was the President of the National Assembly of Togo from September 2000 to February 2005.Les Anciens Présidents de l'Assemblée Nationale - ..::Assemblée Nationale Togolaise:: He was a member of the Rally of the Togolese People (RPT). From 1994 to 2007, he was a member of the National Assembly. From 1992 to 1994, he was Minister of Foreign Affairs. Natchaba died on 15 October 2020 at the age of 75.Togo en deuil : l’ancien Président de l’Assemblée nationale Fambaré Ouattara Natchaba est mort ==References== Category:1945 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Togolese politicians Category:African politicians
